<i>noun</i>: 지뢰 [지뢰/지뤠] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>지뢰 [지뢰/지뤠]</dt><br>
<dd>landmine</dd><br>
<dd>땅속에 묻어 두고 차나 사람이 그 위를 지나가면 폭발하도록 만든 폭약.</dd><br>
<dd>An explosive device that is buried under the ground and designed to explode as vehicles or persons pass over it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>